clientside
1)ssh-keygen (by default all) just passphrase no
2)in home dir of user there will be ~/.shh/  id_rsa.pub
3)cat id_rsa.pub

serverside
passwd - command can generate new passwd for root

1) cd ~ (go to home directory)
2) cd ./ssh
3) nano authorizedkey
4) copy paste the content from id_rsa.pub(from client side who wann login)

